## Part 4 â€“ Enable Required Extensions
1. In IIS â†’ PHP Manager â†’ Enabled:
   - `php_imap.dll`
   - `php_intl.dll`
   - `php_opcache.dll`
2. Refreshed osTicket site and confirmed extensions active.

